snippet.title: BYE-BYE BOXBOY! Launch Trailer - Nintendo 3DS
snippet.description:
Wait…a box is the last defense against annihilation?! Well, fear not—Qbby is no ordinary box. Discover why in this Launch Trailer for his final adventure in the BOXBOY! trilogy.

BYE-BYE BOXBOY! demo and game are Available Now! https://goo.gl/iUZRSJ

#Nintendo3DS #BYEBYEBOXBOY
